{"tid":2038644,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"蓬佩奧：香港不再享有港人治港權利 不再獲得美國特殊待遇","createTime":"2020-05-27T16:17:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T16:17:58.000Z","uid":49669,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e1d0b6274c596165de226989e6f0a1ad9f4b841f","tid":2038644,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T16:17:20.000Z","msg":"美國國務卿蓬佩奧確認香港不再享有港人治港的權利，因此不會像1997年回歸前一樣，獲得美國法例賦予的特殊待遇。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧周三向國會確認香港目前的情況。他在聲明中說：「任何有合理思維的人今日都可斷言，香港不再維持高度自治。」他又說，中國顯然要把香港改造成中國城市一般。<br />\n<br />\n路透社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200527/OVWVNRGP6KYM3D4PE2K6HRNEXU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3nTIQ1nnRgxBTcTQMosyt9B3XNsYglnHjyUkpWlEd5kRmCWrU1NCxuVYo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200527%2FOVWVNRGP6KYM3D4PE2K6HRNEXU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3nTIQ1nnRgxBTcTQMosyt9B3XNsYglnHjyUkpWlEd5kRmCWrU1NCxuVYo&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32aQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=84c0c746\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200527%2FOVWVNRGP6KYM3D4PE2K6HRNEXU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3nTIQ1nnRgxBTcTQMosyt9B3XNsYglnHjyUkpWlEd5kRmCWrU1NCxuVYo&h=2fea82d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200527/OVWVNRGP6KYM3D4PE2K6HRNEXU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3nTIQ1nnRgxBTcTQMosyt9B3XNsYglnHjyUkpWlEd5kRmCWrU1NCxuVYo</a><br />\n<br />\n支爆來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a19041ae7708fecdefc6f6a49afd66f0406894df","tid":2038644,"uid":254788,"like"